  "reasoning": {
    "objective": "Produce the normalized input vector for \"OpenClaw Completion E2E\" from current observations so RE can evaluate its CES sequences.",
    "systemPrompt": "You are the OpenClaw input-analyst agent for the RealityEngine machine \"OpenClaw Completion E2E\".\n\nOBJECTIVE\nReason over the currently available observations and produce a normalized assessment of the machine's input axes. Deterministic integration fixture for proving an ACP dispatch handoff followed by OpenClaw completion ingestion through the Perception Engine.\n\nINPUT AXES (return one value in [0.0, 1.0] for each; anchors define the scale):\n- completed (index 0):  0.0 = pending | 0.5 =  | 1.0 = completed\n- failed (index 1):  0.0 = not failed | 0.5 =  | 1.0 = failed\n- confidence (index 2):  0.0 = no confidence | 0.5 =  | 1.0 = maximum confidence\n- actionClass (index 3):  0.0 = no action | 0.5 =  | 1.0 = action required\n\nWHAT YOUR INPUTS TRIGGER (RE evaluates the CES deterministically; you assert your expectation, RE decides):\n- openclaw-e2e-dispatch-seed (AMBER)\n- openclaw-e2e-completion-accepted (GREEN)",
    "outputContract": "Return one structured line per input axis as `<axis_key>: <0.0-1.0>`, then `asserted_sequence: <sequenceId>`, `confidence: <low|moderate|high|0-1>`, and `rationale: <one sentence>`. RE re-evaluates the CES from the written input vector and is authoritative for which sequence fires.",
    "inputAxes": [
      {
        "index": 0,
        "key": "completed",
        "anchors": {
          "low": "pending",
          "mid": "",
          "high": "completed"
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1,
        "key": "failed",
        "anchors": {
          "low": "not failed",
          "mid": "",
          "high": "failed"
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "key": "confidence",
        "anchors": {
          "low": "no confidence",
          "mid": "",
          "high": "maximum confidence"
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "key": "actionClass",
        "anchors": {
          "low": "no action",
          "mid": "",
          "high": "action required"
        }
      }
    ],
    "sequenceCatalog": [
      {
        "sequenceId": "openclaw-e2e-dispatch-seed",
        "label": "openclaw-e2e-dispatch-seed",
        "rag": "AMBER",
        "outputIndex": 0,
        "action": ""
      },
      {
        "sequenceId": "openclaw-e2e-completion-accepted",
        "label": "openclaw-e2e-completion-accepted",
        "rag": "GREEN",
        "outputIndex": 3,
        "action": ""
      }
    ]
  },
  "agentBinding": {
